<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <title>IgAN Progression Simulator - Hypothetical Patient Cases</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn more about IgAN through interactive patient cases. Follow their treatment journey and determine the risk of progression based on their unique traits">
  {{> ../templates/header }}
  <link href="../styles.bundle.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
  <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-WZLFQZR3" height="0" width="0"
      style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
  <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
  <main class="wrapper" data-page-id="progression" data-path-level="1">

    {{> ../templates/nav }}
    {{> ../templates/interstitial }}

    <div class="progression-content content-container">
      <h1>IgA肾病疾病进展模拟</h1>
      <h2 class="subhead">认识虚拟患者莎拉、卡洛斯和马克，深入了解他们的lgAN患病历程</h2>

      <div class="profiles-container">
        <div class="profile-option nav-el" data-nav-url="progression/sarah">
          <div>
            <img src="./assets/images/profiles/sarah-profile.png" class="update-path profile-pic"
              alt="" />

            <h3 class="name">莎拉 (25)</h3>
            <p>上呼吸道感染后出现血尿和蛋白尿</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <p class="link-style">了解更多关于莎拉的情况</p>
            <img src="./assets/images/arrow-dark.svg" class="update-path" alt="Dark arrow pointing right" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-option nav-el" data-nav-url="progression/carlos">
          <div>
            <img src="./assets/images/profiles/carlos-profile.png" class="update-path profile-pic"
              alt="" />

            <h3 class="name">卡洛斯 (40)</h3>
            <p>主诉疲劳、体重增加和脚踝水肿</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <p class="link-style">了解更多关于卡洛斯的情况</p>
            <img src="./assets/images/arrow-dark.svg" class="update-path" alt="Dark arrow pointing right" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-option nav-el" data-nav-url="progression/mark">
          <div>
            <img src="./assets/images/profiles/mark-profile.png" class="update-path profile-pic"
              alt="" />

            <h3 class="name">马克 (34)</h3>
            <p>出现血尿及泡沫尿</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <p class="link-style">了解更多关于马克的情况</p>
            <img src="./assets/images/arrow-dark.svg" class="update-path" alt="Dark arrow pointing right" />
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> ../templates/footer-el }}

  </main>

  <script type="text/javascript" src="../static.bundle.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
</body>

</html>